SYSEXT_INVALID_DICTIONARY.target: System extension %@ has an invalid CMIOExtension key in its Info.plist: the value of the CMIOExtension key must be a non-empty dictionary.

SYSEXT_INVALID_MACH_SERVICE_NAME.target: System extension %@ has an invalid mach service name or is not signed, the value must be prefixed with one of the App Groups in the entitlement.

SYSEXT_CANNOT_READ_BUNDLE.target: Failed to load the system extension bundle at %@.

SYSEXT_INTERNAL_ERROR.target: System extension %@ could not be started because an internal error occurred.
